---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  altLangHref="/fr/about"
  title="About - Killian Perzo"
  description="Learn about my journey: Data Scientist specialized in Agentic AI at Median Technologies. Expert in multi-agent systems, LangChain, LangGraph."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8 sm:py-16 px-4 sm:px-0">
    <div class="mb-8 sm:mb-12">
      <p class="font-body text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-gold mb-3">About</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-charcoal dark:text-white leading-tight">
        My <span class="gold-accent">journey</span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-5 sm:space-y-6">
      <p class="font-body text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Hi, I'm <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white font-semibold">Killian</strong> — Data Scientist passionate about <span class="text-gold font-semibold">Agentic AI</span>, <span class="text-gold font-semibold">multi-agent systems</span>, and <span class="text-gold font-semibold">building autonomous agents</span>.
      </p>

      <p class="font-body text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        After studying Sports Science (STAPS) and completing a Bachelor's in Data Science, I pursued a Master's in Data Analysis, which I will finish by the end of 2025. I currently work at <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">Median Technologies</strong>, where I've developed intelligent automation solutions and AI applied to medical imaging.
      </p>

      <div class="p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-800/60 border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-gray-700/30 backdrop-blur-sm border-l-[3px] border-l-gold">
        <p class="font-body text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          My specialty: designing <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">intelligent autonomous agents</strong> capable of reasoning, collaborating, and executing complex tasks. I use frameworks like <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">LangChain</strong>, <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">LangGraph</strong>, and advanced LLMs (Claude, GPT) to build RAG systems, multi-agent workflows, and intelligent automation tools.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="font-body text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        On the personal side, I created <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">DataSentinel AI</strong> — an intelligent monitoring system using autonomous agents to analyze and monitor data pipelines. I'm also developing <strong class="text-charcoal dark:text-white">Data Quality Agent</strong>, a specialized agent for automated data quality analysis with intelligent report generation.
      </p>

      <p class="font-body text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        My goal? To build AI agents that augment human intelligence and automate complex tasks. I'm looking for opportunities to develop high-impact agentic AI systems, where agent autonomy enables solving real-world problems at scale.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary btn-icon text-center">
        <span>Contact me</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/en/cv" class="btn-secondary text-center">View my resume</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
